{"tid":1515092,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"以後唔需要再申請不反對通知書 訂好詳情 做好文宣 自然有人嚟","createTime":"2019-08-29T04:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T08:55:34.000Z","uid":135891,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b44745aba2d6939e10d5ef81b91a8c7423fe260","tid":1515092,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:00:37.000Z","msg":"發得夢 個個都匿名 冇理由漏低搞手係到單打獨鬥 比狗咬 比鄉黑打<br />\n<br />\n係公眾地方自由活動係人類應有嘅權利<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不反對通知書本身就係臨時立法會為咗反人權而重新訂立</span></strong> <br />\n我地既然爭取人權自由 就毋須再肯定不反對通知書制度<br />\n香港人要進化到唔好再理有冇不反對通知書 <span style=\"color: red;\">正義之事不需要被不反對</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要團結 我們必勝<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"7a61cccdc62eb7069a98b2095a5ab5c033df7d8a","tid":1515092,"uid":191271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:01:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1515044\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1515044</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入黎投票<br />\n<br />\n「連登共識」 8 3 1 遊 行 宣言"},{"pid":"5dd32fa7b16a8105007863f2edadff7452cbf732","tid":1515092,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"不反對通知書本身就係臨時立法會為咗反人權而重新訂立"},{"pid":"697223c57a897fe5843ae9c9df6f87351f296fa8","tid":1515092,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"076119328ffa3a9ca057fb1e0b6c09cc494f7468","tid":1515092,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:32:01.000Z","msg":"反對通知書都係照出點解仲要申請"},{"pid":"f4e25a25b29539983cc7b7a7690481b866982092","tid":1515092,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:34:24.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n831 中環見"},{"pid":"4a496bee0eb2574939e49f5c1cf767a695bc754b","tid":1515092,"ui